# Deploy targets

## Default (always)

- **Develop and deploy only in `sheetomatic-redesign`** → production **Sheetomatic** (`sheetomatic.com` / `app.sheetomatic.com`).
- Commit, push `main`, and Vercel verify for Sheetomatic unless the user **explicitly** names another target.

## Named exceptions only

Deploy or push to **Hingorani** or **Tops** **only** when the user clearly says so, e.g.:

- "deploy on Hingorani"
- "deploy to Tops"
- "push Hingorani portal"

Do **not** infer Hingorani/Tops from context (legal cases, client names in chat, dedicated portals in code) unless the user names the deploy target in that message.

## Do not

- Push Sheetomatic changes to Hingorani/Tops repos or Vercel projects by default.
- Run release-ops or multitask deploy workers for Hingorani/Tops without an explicit user request.
- Treat `hingorani.sheetomatic.com` or other dedicated subdomains as a deploy instruction unless the user asks to deploy there.

## When ambiguous

Ask: *"Deploy to Sheetomatic only, or to Hingorani/Tops?"* — default answer is Sheetomatic.
